subject: Payment Receipt — {{ booking_id }}
<h2>Payment Received</h2>
<p>Dear {{ customer_name }},</p>
<p>Your payment of <strong>{{ amount }}</strong> for booking <strong>{{ booking_id }}</strong> at {{ hub_name }} has been received.</p>
<table>
  <tr><td><strong>Payment Method:</strong></td><td>{{ payment_method }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Amount:</strong></td><td>{{ amount }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Date:</strong></td><td>{{ date }}</td></tr>
</table>
<p>Thank you for your payment. Ride safely!</p>
